Deploy Suricata Rules with Zeek for Layer 7 Visibility
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure Suricata IDS for signature-based detection
Deploy Zeek network security monitor for behavioral analysis
Create custom Layer 7 detection rules for application protocols
Integrate both tools for comprehensive network visibility
Develop Python automation scripts for log analysis and monitoring
Prerequisites
Basic Linux command line proficiency
Understanding of TCP/IP and common protocols (HTTP, DNS, TLS)
Familiarity with network security concepts
Basic Python programming skills
